1. "Čekali smo da nam puste *pustili* unutra (We waited for them to let us in.) 
2. Oni su *pustili* psa da trči (They let the dog run.)
3. Oni su *pustili* svoje stvari u njegovu kuću (They let their things in his house.) 
4. Oni su *pustili* da se čuje njihov glas (They let their voice be heard.)
5. Oni su *pustili* loptu (They released the ball.) 
6. Oni su *pustili* vodu da teče (They let the water run.)